- Hey, how are you, guys?
- Erin!

01:35.965 --> 01:37.140
- Hi!

01:37.184 --> 01:38.446
How are you?
- How are you, girl?

01:38.489 --> 01:40.404
- Good to see you.
- Good to see you!

01:40.448 --> 01:41.449
What are you guys doing?

01:41.492 --> 01:42.711
- You're gonna see in a minute.

01:42.754 --> 01:44.234
I need some help.

01:44.278 --> 01:45.583
- We need help.
- My brother-in-law,

01:45.627 --> 01:47.019
I need some help.
- Oh, really?

01:47.063 --> 01:48.369
- Bad.
- Lots of help?

01:48.412 --> 01:49.326
- Well, we're trying.
-

01:49.370 --> 01:50.327
- Yeah, well, lots of help.

01:50.371 --> 01:51.546
We're trying to get him used

01:51.589 --> 01:52.938
to this whole Texas lifestyle,
right?

01:52.982 --> 01:54.940
- Set my purse down.
- And just wait. You'll see.

01:54.984 --> 01:56.986
- Right now Noah and Lacey
are spending, you know,

01:57.029 --> 01:58.596
50 percent of their time
in Hawaii

