of your current shoes?

02:40.856 --> 02:42.771
- They're just
toughening you up.

02:42.814 --> 02:44.816
Getting you a thick skin
for Texas.

02:44.860 --> 02:45.948
Suck it up, buttercup.

02:48.037 --> 02:49.081
- Okay.

02:49.125 --> 02:50.213
Now that sounded pretty good.

02:50.257 --> 02:51.997
We want a little thud.
- Okay.

02:52.041 --> 02:53.173
- Stand up on that.

02:53.216 --> 02:54.304
So just kinda
take a spin in those

02:54.348 --> 02:55.305
and just see what you think.

02:55.349 --> 02:56.263
